title: Archie's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Delivery, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu features mostly vegetarian dishes. Uses a variety of fresh vegetables or fruits. Also has fresh squeezed orange juice, fresh pineapple or strawberry juice, and jugo verde (a vegetable juice mix). Free Wi-Fi. Clean, casual atmosphere. As of June 2014, only one clearly marked vegan dish on the menu, but other dishes could be made vegan; just ask.
